{"tid":995227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡漢偷拍女同事裙底　犯賤影片讓人硬了","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T09:34:49.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6939ba35dfa5897d0280d5b165d2cbba58f3c73f","tid":995227,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"據英國《太陽報》報導，從一輛車子的行車紀錄器上可見，兩名男子和一名女子走在地下停車場裡，相信3人是熟識的關係。但這時也看到一名揹著包包、走在最後面的男子，居然拿著手機，沿路一直偷拍旁邊女同事的裙底風光，整個過程女子完全不知情，另外一名男子也沒有注意到，隨即與其他兩人道別後離去。<br />\n目前未知這名偷拍癡漢有無被逮捕，但新加坡近年來偷拍案件有增加的趨勢，根據新加坡法令，製作、複製及散佈淫穢影片，屬非法行為，違者最高可處4萬新加坡幣(約新台幣91萬元)及2年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190125/1507034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190125%2F1507034&d=Ev%2FgGGd3hbiNhm%2BUCJXp8GowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=36d2c872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190125%2F1507034&h=9e8dfbb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190125/1507034</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190125/640_255d8a842f2cb4b21411206106721709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190125%2F640_255d8a842f2cb4b21411206106721709.jpg&h=ed4ce4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5-6秒，勁"}]}